2:T739,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Lumen5 better than Runway ML?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Lumen5 scores 6.0 overall while Runway ML scores 9.0. Lumen5 is best for content marketers and repurposing blog content to video, while Runway ML excels for filmmakers and creatives and AI video generation pioneers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Lumen5 or Runway ML?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lumen5 starts at $19/mo and Runway ML starts at $12/mo. Lumen5 offers a free plan. Runway ML offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Lumen5 to Runway ML?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Lumen5 and Runway ML support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Lumen5 vs Runway ML?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Lumen5 holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10. Runway ML has an overall rating of 9/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Lumen5 for blog-to-video automation and Runway ML for industry-leading gen-3 video quality."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Lumen5 or Runway ML?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Runway ML for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Lumen5 remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize blog-to-video automation. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML