7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Lumen5 and Runway ML share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Video. Where Lumen5 pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Auto Captions and Templates and Stock Footage and Voice Over, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Runway ML uniquely offers Image To Video and Api Access, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Lumen5 holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Runway ML scores 9/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Runway ML comes in at a lower starting price of $12/mo, while Lumen5 begins at $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Lumen5's free tier and Runway ML's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
