b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Lumen5 is best suited for content marketers, repurposing blog content to video, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Runway ML, meanwhile, shines for filmmakers and creatives, AI video generation pioneers, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, Lumen5 describes itself as \"Turn blog posts and articles into engaging videos.\" Runway ML, established in 2018, positions itself as \"AI-powered creative tools for video generation and editing.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Runway ML** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (9.0 vs 6.0), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Lumen5 is a poor choice — far from it. Lumen5 excels in its own right, particularly for content marketers and repurposing blog content to video.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value industry-leading gen-3 video quality, go with Runway ML. If blog-to-video automation matters more to you, Lumen5 is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
